{"tid":310764,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"（孝感動天）點樣說服阿媽去旅行","createTime":"2017-07-06T05:29:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-06T08:16:01.000Z","uid":74850,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d2a44eba68a47dd973e3428be6386ffe4809c050","tid":310764,"uid":74850,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T05:29:16.000Z","msg":"自己好鐘意旅行。做野幾年，去左唔少地方，好想搵機會帶埋兩老一齊去。但自從阿媽跟團去過一次台灣，俾d sales sell左好多又貴又冇用既手信之後，就唔搵再出遊，覺得好哂錢。<br />\n<br />\n今年年尾至新年，想帶兩老去日本，呢次唔會跟團，由我安排。應該點說服佢地一齊去？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98b18270d234a93eb5752e8c9bf9571e7d708cd6","tid":310764,"uid":65376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T05:33:03.000Z","msg":"同佢講你升職 要出國賀一賀佢"},{"pid":"c9aee30990444caa77b8f916b5ad558d10c134ab","tid":310764,"uid":65376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T05:34:09.000Z","msg":"同老豆講帶佢去日本見識av<br />\n同老母講帶佢去買野食同化妝品"},{"pid":"80b5627b13b1aeb732bc26a77a8df39e43d983a9","tid":310764,"uid":100353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T05:35:00.000Z","msg":"你同呀媽講去日本結婚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe90fb4d1383076bd3a236ed487948c5855b0ade","tid":310764,"uid":72908,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T05:35:58.000Z","msg":"去打柒d 日本仔，當時侵華搞到咁慘"},{"pid":"2c667485aaf0a0eb552818335f5b6bd0f5b2ebca","tid":310764,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T05:38:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>自己好鐘意旅行。做野幾年，去左唔少地方，好想搵機會帶埋兩老一齊去。但自從阿媽跟團去過一次台灣，俾d sales sell左好多又貴又冇用既手信之後，就唔搵再出遊，覺得好哂錢。<br />\n<br />\n今年年尾至新年，想帶兩老去日本，呢次唔會跟團，由我安排。應該點說服佢地一齊去？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n嘩<br />\n帶兩老去日本自由行，你打算坐地鐵？<br />\n我試過，好煩下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68f8059366b014f9d0a1f7218f71691ef6c1ae9a","tid":310764,"uid":44118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T05:41:36.000Z","msg":"先斬後奏"},{"pid":"d43ec19b2368dd1b0fc44451a845186a49c10c09","tid":310764,"uid":74850,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T05:42:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同佢講你升職 要出國賀一賀佢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n年尾過probation, 依家未升到<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"635b65cffa4dac29f7aafdf7995513646fbd07e1","tid":310764,"uid":74850,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T05:42:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>自己好鐘意旅行。做野幾年，去左唔少地方，好想搵機會帶埋兩老一齊去。但自從阿媽跟團去過一次台灣，俾d sales sell左好多又貴又冇用既手信之後，就唔搵再出遊，覺得好哂錢。<br />\n<br />\n今年年尾至新年，想帶兩老去日本，呢次唔會跟團，由我安排。應該點說服佢地一齊去？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n嘩<br />\n帶兩老去日本自由行，你打算坐地鐵？<br />\n我試過，好煩下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打可唔可以分享下經驗"},{"pid":"c02a4e60f727f539e57dca5f91ca5521bda95d64","tid":310764,"uid":111343,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T08:15:02.000Z","msg":"問定佢地幾時得閒(可以唔洗咁精確 例如你8月有無野約人牙咁) 之後直接買機票<br />\n<br />\n我果時同阿媽細佬都想一齊去 但我老豆唔肯去 <br />\n最尾買埋曬成家人機票訂埋酒店同幫佢Book埋整埋passport先去到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8cc36c637f7c3e7b553b2da872e19152d675850d","tid":310764,"uid":111343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T08:16:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>問定佢地幾時得閒(可以唔洗咁精確 例如你8月有無野約人牙咁) 之後直接買機票<br />\n<br />\n我果時同阿媽細佬都想一齊去 但我老豆唔肯去 <br />\n最尾買埋曬成家人機票訂埋酒店同幫佢Book埋整埋passport先去到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">呀</span> 自<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}